marginalia.translation:
[If] you left him at the other house and you advance to the place at first,
it is either detrimental or favourable to you
[?]
Ask his name and [?] consider the letter of his name.
and if it is a, e, i, o, u, good will come to you;
and if it is b, m, k, s, you will find and you will lose;
and if it is c, d, q, [?] death, misfortune or injury;
if it is x, r, p, you will find joy in your life;
if it is l, y, you will have what you seek;
if it is g, f, it signifies a bad situation.
